data.description: Opportunity knocks! Located in SIERRA LOMA, NW Reno's premier condo development, this highly desirable single level home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a direct access 2 car garage. The large, very private deck is accessible from the living/dining area and primary bedroom. There is a gated courtyard at the front door and no common walls with surrounding homes. The furnace and water heater are new, fresh exterior paint and new roof. The price reflects the need for cosmetic work, but the reward will be great!
